*zile-2.0.7 (06 Jul 2005)

  06 Jul 2005; Matthew Kennedy <mkennedy@gentoo.org> +zile-2.0.7.ebuild:
  New upstream version; Resolves Bug #98062

  21 Apr 2005; Simon Stelling <blubb@gentoo.org> zile-1.7_beta3-r1.ebuild:
  stable on amd64

  05 Mar 2005; Mamoru KOMACHI <usata@gentoo.org> zile-2.0.0.ebuild:
  Changed to use libtermcap-compat; bug #82674.
  Thanks to keith+gentoo@merelyclay.com.

*zile-2.0.0 (11 Feb 2005)

  11 Feb 2005; Mamoru KOMACHI <usata@gentoo.org> -zile-1.7_alpha6.ebuild,
